{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "credbuzz-rbac-collection",
		"name": "CredBuzz Backend API",
		"description": "Complete API collection for CredBuzz Backend including User Authentication and RBAC (Role-Based Access Control) endpoints.\n\n## Dynamic Login\nLogin uses a single `identifier` field that auto-detects:\n- **Email**: Contains @ (e.g., user@example.com)\n- **Phone**: Starts with + (e.g., +1234567890)\n- **User Code**: 6 alphanumeric chars (e.g., CGX0R0)\n- **Username**: Default fallback\n\n## Login Security\n- Progressive lockout: 5 attempts ‚Üí 2min ‚Üí 5min ‚Üí 10min ‚Üí 30min ‚Üí 60min ‚Üí blocked\n- Session inactivity timeout: 30 minutes (like bank apps)\n- JWT includes: user_code, user_role, app_access, feature_access\n\n## User Roles\n- **DEVELOPER**: System developer (highest privilege) - Created via CLI\n- **SUPER_ADMIN**: Super administrator - Created via CLI with Developer authorization\n- **ADMIN**: Administrator - Register + role assignment by Super Admin\n- **CLIENT**: Client user - Register + role assignment by Admin+\n- **END_USER**: End user (default) - Self-registration\n\n## User Code\nEvery user has a unique 6-character alphanumeric code (e.g., ABC123) auto-generated at creation.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
