							"raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/users/3/hard-delete/",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["auth", "users", "3", "hard-delete", ""]
						},
						"description": "**HARD DELETE** - Permanently removes user from database.\n\n‚ö†Ô∏è **WARNING:** This action CANNOT be undone!\n\n- Completely removes user record\n- Removes all related data (sessions, login attempts, etc.)\n- User cannot be recovered\n\n**Note:** Cannot delete your own account."
					},
					"response": []
				},
